JPEG XS Rust Implementation - Hybrid License Model

================================================================================
DUAL-TRACK LICENSING STRUCTURE
================================================================================

This project contains two distinct tracks with different licensing:

1. EVALUATION TRACK (`crates/` directory)
   - Contains derivative work from reference implementation
   - Copyright: intoPIX SA, Fraunhofer IIS, Canon Inc (derivative portions)
   - Copyright: Keyvan Ebrahimpour (original Rust portions)
   - License: Evaluation and testing only
   - Commercial use: Requires RAND license from original copyright holders

2. COMMERCIAL TRACK (`commercial/` directory)
   - Contains ONLY clean-room implementations
   - Copyright: Keyvan Ebrahimpour (2024)
   - License: Proprietary with commercial licensing available
   - Commercial use: Available under separate agreement

